@host = http://localhost:19200

### CHECK HEALTH
GET {{host}}

###

### =====================================
### 2. CREATE INDEX + MAPPING (JOBS)
### =====================================
PUT {{host}}/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

< ./job.mapping.json

###

### =====================================
### 2. DELETE INDEX (JOBS)
### =====================================
DELETE {{host}}/jobs

